                <h2>What users may request</h2>
            </div>
            <ul class="privacy-page-list">
                <li>Request access to personal information held in relation to the platform.</li>
                <li>Request correction of inaccurate or outdated personal information.</li>
                <li>Request deletion, blocking, or limitation where appropriate and legally permitted.</li>
                <li>Raise concerns about how personal information is being used.</li>
                <li>Ask for clarification when a workflow or notice is unclear.</li>
            </ul>
        </article>

